  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7e99d2aa6db43f2478d3198a0ca05313, type: 3}
  m_Name: Level 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueInfo:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "So\u2026 my guest here is really a professional, huh?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "If that\u2019s the case, why have I never heard of you before? Don\u2019t
      you use social media or something?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 1
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "It\u2019s \u2018cuz I have only started, duh. Bold of you to think
      that I\u2019m already famous."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: 
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Ha! Hahaha! Holy! Hahahahahahahahahaha~!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Oh I\u2019m dying!"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Hahaha\u2026 Ha\u2026 Ha\u2026"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "\u201CAre you done?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Almost\u2026"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Ha\u2026 Haaaa\u2026"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Okay. I\u2019m done."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Wow. That was some real laughter you did there.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "That\u2019s because you talked like you have had decades of experience!
      You really had me, you know?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Well, we all have to start from somewhere, right
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: True
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: So I chose your vendor to be the starting point of my career.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "I get to be a food critic and you get free advertisements. That\u2019s
      a win-win situation, don\u2019t you think?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Alright. You got me. It\u2019s a deal then."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Sooo\u2026. Mr. Professional Food Critic, what should I call you?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "*Name changed*, huh? An \u201Cinteresting\u201D choice for a name
      there."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: " \u201CWhat? You don\u2019t think it\u2019s good?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "It\u2019s cool. It\u2019s cool. It's up to you to decide after all."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "Ooh\u2026kay."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "Oh yeah, I noticed that you don\u2019t just sell B\xE1nh M\xEC, right?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Yep. I sell Ch\xE8 Hu\u1EBF and-"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: "Sweet! I\u2019ll have one of that as well if you don\u2019t mind."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Sure thing, mate. Coming right up.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Oh and be sure to \u201Ccritic\u201D it as well, yeah?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Gotcha.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "So\u2026 how was it?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Holy moly! That was so good!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: The flavours of the mixed beans compliment each other so well that
      I could taste all of them without the feeling like they were fighting each
      other at all.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Hahaha!
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Look at you! You really enjoyed my dessert that much, huh?
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Of course! How could anyone not enjoy this?
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: Then your review better be good about it.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b3301c203e1570d4baea337fddfeacfa, type: 2}
    charText: "Otherwise, I\u2019m gonna punch you in the face. Hahaha."
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dcbb5bf5c792b71498b2fb1c38ad7fd7, type: 2}
    charText: Alright! You got it.
    characterEmotion: 0
    continueCheck: 0
